      propertyPath: interactLabel
      value: F - Case Files
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: continueButton
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 914400631}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: interactButton
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1161615709}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: interactButtonText
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1412500810}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogues.Array.size
      value: 7
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: playerMovementScript
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1455371406}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: setHasInteractedSwitch
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[0]'
      value: "Theft\u2026 fraud\u2026 arson\u2026. It\u2019s just another mountain
        of files to climb today\u2026 It never really ends, doesn't it?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[1]'
      value: "Oh... What\u2019s this doing here? It\u2019s so thin\u2026 No label,
        just this nonsensical scribbling all over the cove\u2026 That\u2019s\u2026
        actually quite unnerving\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[2]'
      value: "Why does it feel so heavy in my hands? It\u2019s like the paper itself
        is weighted down by something I can't see."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[3]'
      value: "A murder case\u2026 This must be the one I saw from outside... Hmmm\u2026
        As I said before, I usually go out of my way to avoid these\u2026 "
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[4]'
      value: "But look at this, the details are so precise, so clean\u2026 It\u2019s
        almost\u2026 Too neat. Why does this feel so eerily familiar to me?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[5]'
      value: "This... case\u2026 it really caught my interest\u2026 Coincidentally,
        I\u2019m also quite familiar with the area\u2026 Hmmm..."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[6]'
      value: "I must investigate this immediately\u2026 starting by going to that
        neighborhood\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[7]'
      value: '*closes the file slowly*'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[8]'
      value: A son killing his father with no reason anyone can explain... There's
        more to this than what's on paper.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[9]'
      value: 'This is my case now. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[10]'
      value: I should go there now using my car
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[11]'
      value: I should go there now using my car
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7207236140021446596, guid: 173e3fc1830a64c4c828c2779d64dac1, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogues.Array.data[12]'
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
