      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Sir! You're here, finally.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Hey, want some coffee? I just brewed a fresh pot.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Thanks Jam, but I'll make my own.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: You know how I like it.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Suit yourself.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Oh, before you head to your office...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: "Fair warning \u2014 there's quite the stack of case files waiting for
        you in there."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Yeah, Yanzie mentioned something about that.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: I'll take a look.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Good luck. You're going to need it.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
